{"tid":1535653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「我要申請人身保護令！」無人識用既？","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T18:42:22.000Z","uid":282650,"like":89,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"41ce26e35c03eff7c9afd13c87092c8ad20e9121","tid":1535653,"uid":282650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:26:25.000Z","msg":"而家黑警下下扣人48小時先放人，但連最基本要拘捕一個人既條件都無，即係「合理懷疑」一個人犯法呀。<br />\n有個基本人權大家都無用呀，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「人身保護令」</span></span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n「人身保護令」HabeasCorpus拉丁文的意思是「你應帶同該人人身」。設若有人指稱被當權者非法羈留，該人即可向原訟法庭申請發出人身保護令狀，要求羈留他的人向法庭說明拘押的理據。這申請可由被羈留的人提出，或由任何人代他提出。原訟法庭會視這類案件為最迫切而需要優先聆訊的案件。 <br />\n涉及「人身保護令狀」的法律程序，均須在公開法庭進行，除非在例外情況下，法官可命令聆訊或部份聆訊在內庭進行。但即使在這類情況下，所有法庭的命令及裁決，以及作出該命令或裁決的理由，都必須公開在法庭上宣布。因此，傳媒亦可報道該項聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲黎講，根據人權法案5（4）條，被拉既人可以即時要求法庭審視佢係咪被非法拘留。<br />\n即使唔係自己，其他人都可以代佢向高院原訟庭申請，法庭要優先處理！<br />\n法庭接納後要立即發出命令叫黑警帶人上庭問佢原因，黑警當刻就要講，事後就無得改答案，未作好故仔好大機會就要放人架啦，仲要同全世界講自己非法拘禁呀！<br />\n泛民律師唔該幫手做下呢樣野，而家太多濫捕程況，被拉後要盡快做呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap4!zh-Hant-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap4%21zh-Hant-HK&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDZhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=0378656c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap4!zh-Hant-HK</a><br />\n法例第4章22A條有寫架！<br />\n<br />\n覺得有用就代推，推到有人成功要黑警放人！"},{"pid":"9f26eed449385039dd5e636f764635bd782ab923","tid":1535653,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b73665e16de30222f2de08a4fde2ba08202e6054","tid":1535653,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"支那毅進仔撚識咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d3f197c6af5e68b9f3f16c202bccd8e2843747","tid":1535653,"uid":81385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"黑警會話調查中不上庭再嘈官都拉埋"},{"pid":"4a35858c5f0f78603051a75fd8416fbe03b594ce","tid":1535653,"uid":94640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b73665e16de30222f2de08a4fde2ba08202e6054","tid":1535653,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"支那毅進仔撚識咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"法庭傳召佢冇得say no"},{"pid":"5e53afe8944cd7a872af7a10d8e533521e892385","tid":1535653,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:34:20.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"8c71e35ea18609289e572dfa6c142b7016410f45","tid":1535653,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4767945d28af781888773705c4521dd93fa166e1","tid":1535653,"uid":94640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0